H0.text: What city is considered the birthplace of jazz music. Chicago

H1.text: What city is considered the birthplace of jazz music. Kansas City

H2.text: What city is considered the birthplace of jazz music. St. Louis

H3.text: What city is considered the birthplace of jazz music. NOLA

A4.text: Jazz originated in the African-American communities of New Orleans, Louisiana, in the late 19th and early 20th centuries.

A5.text: New Orleans jazz began in the early 1910s, combining earlier brass band marches, French quadrilles, biguine, ragtime and blues with collective polyphonic improvisation.
